data.description: Don't miss out on this fixer upper with so much investment potential! The cottage is situated on a great corner lot on a quaint street in Arnaudville. The home features three bedroom and two bathrooms with an open floor plan, space to add an island and large utility room. Scoop this one up and make it yours!Short Sale is being professionally processed by Universal Short Sales, LLC. Buyer Responsible for Short Sale Processing Fee of $10,000. Please review ''Presentation ofOffers'' document before submitting offer. Property sold as-is.
